This is a MU-Faust power suit.  Its named faust cause it trades the users own life force for enhanced abilities and such.  It will appear in an upcoming book on my site in more detail but for now lets do this challenge thing.  <br>
<br>
The Neo Prometheus city govt is holding a corperate tournement.  Various engineering companies were to design these power suits and pit them in combat.  The winners prototype gets mass produced and used as a method of control in Pro-city (Police like).  <br>
<br>
The Arena:  Old Prometheus city, long destroyed by the war past, its mostly a wasteland with a few pockets of life.  Lots of crime in the area, but the tournetakes place in a building district long destroyed.<br>
<br>
The Rules:  FCs are fun ^_^, but there is no way to decide how it should end. So lets play with it a lil.  You get 250 points.  Draw your powersuit, design your pilot (team) if you like.  The points need to be directed towards its armor and weapon systems.  Each weapon does the dmg points that it was given.  But weapons have a heat or payload limit, so i you use it for like 3 panels in a row its hot or needs a reload.  Save for hand to hand weapons.  <br>
<br>
Anal Stuff:  Dont put someone elses unit in a dumb position that nobody would do just get get maximum potential out of your weapon.  If you want maximize potential use your ability as a layout artist and cleer battle scripter to get the other combatant into position.<br>
  Individual parts can be destroyed.  Anything with a weapon or advantage giving mechanism on it MUST have a set dmg point.  <br>
  Even if you draw another person using their weapon for a panels sake.  It doesnt count as them using it unless the PERSON WHO CREATED THE SUIT draws it.  So if you draw them shooting beam cannon 001 like 5 times it still wont over heat.  In turn it also wont do any (official dmg) to any other character.  AS in you may draw it someone elses character doing dmg and looking cool but unless the artist of that bot draws the attack it doesnt count.  <br>
  Armor is armor, but shields are shields.  A shield must fully depleted before anyindividual body part may be destroyed...in turn, no shield may be stronget then 50 points....but armor points you can waste as many as you want on.<br>
  Mechs should be no bigger then 10 feet tall.  Mine is only 7<br>
<br>
....phew, i think i got it all.  Any questions just post it and ill see it.  limit is 5-6 peeps hope to see you on the battle field.    <p>On a long enough timeline,the survival rate for everyone drops to zero

